<h1 class="text-center">Welcome to CarBNB</h1>
<p class="text-center"> CarBNB is a car rental marketplace that connects car owners with people who need a car for a short period of time. </p>
<% if user_signed_in? %>
  <p class="text-center"> Start browsing all cars below! </p>
  <div class="text-center">
    <%= link_to "View all cars", cars_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
<% else %>
  <p class="text-center"> Click on <strong>Sign up / Log in in top left </strong> and get started! </p>
<% end %>
